# fields.prompt

**Fields for herobanner**
1. selectableVariant (string) - used for choosing a variant (default or xDemo).
2. title (string) - main heading text.
3. subtitle (string) - secondary heading text.
4. imageUrl (url) - optional background or hero image link.
5. altText (string) - alt text for the hero image.
6. sortOrder (number) - to determine the order of this component on the page.
7. globalComponentSource (reference) - references a global herobanner if needed.